INNER JOIN [Designations] AS [d0] ON [e].[DesignationId] = [d0].[DesignationId]

) AS [t] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t].[EmployeeId]

FROM [Employees] AS [e]
INNER JOIN [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [d].[EmployeeId]
INNER JOIN [Designations] AS [d0] ON [e].[DesignationId] = [d0].[DesignationId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d2].[DepartmentName], [d1].[EmployeeId], [d1].[DepartmentId], [d2].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]
    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d1]
    INNER JOIN [Departments] AS [d2] ON [d1].[DepartmentId] = [d2].[DepartmentId]
) AS [t] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t].[EmployeeId]

    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d3]
    INNER JOIN [Departments] AS [d4] ON [d3].[DepartmentId] = [d4].[DepartmentId]
) AS [t0] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t0].[EmployeeId]

) AS [t1] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t1].[EmployeeId]

SELECT [e].[EmployeeId], [e].[EmployeeName], [e].[EmployeeAddress], [e].[EmployeeSalary], [d0].[DesignationName], [d0].[DesignationCode], [e].[DesignationId], [d].[EmployeeId], [d].[DepartmentId], [d0].[DesignationId], [t].[DepartmentName], [t].[EmployeeId], [t].[DepartmentId], [t].[DepartmentId0], [t0].[DepartmentCode], [t0].[EmployeeId], [t0].[DepartmentId], [t0].[DepartmentId0], [t1].[DepartmentId], [t1].[EmployeeId], [t1].[DepartmentId0]
FROM [Employees] AS [e]
INNER JOIN [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [d].[EmployeeId]
INNER JOIN [Designations] AS [d0] ON [e].[DesignationId] = [d0].[DesignationId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d2].[DepartmentName], [d1].[EmployeeId], [d1].[DepartmentId], [d2].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]
    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d1]
    INNER JOIN [Departments] AS [d2] ON [d1].[DepartmentId] = [d2].[DepartmentId]
) AS [t] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t].[EmployeeId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d4].[DepartmentCode], [d3].[EmployeeId], [d3].[DepartmentId], [d4].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]
    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d3]
    INNER JOIN [Departments] AS [d4] ON [d3].[DepartmentId] = [d4].[DepartmentId]
) AS [t0] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t0].[EmployeeId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d6].[DepartmentId], [d5].[EmployeeId], [d5].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]
    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d5]
    INNER JOIN [Departments] AS [d6] ON [d5].[DepartmentId] = [d6].[DepartmentId]
) AS [t1] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t1].[EmployeeId]

SELECT [e].[EmployeeId], [e].[EmployeeName], [e].[EmployeeAddress], [e].[EmployeeSalary], [d0].[DesignationName], [d0].[DesignationCode], [e].[DesignationId], [d].[EmployeeId], [d].[DepartmentId], [d0].[DesignationId], [t].[DepartmentName], [t].[EmployeeId], [t].[DepartmentId], [t].[DepartmentId0], [t0].[DepartmentCode], [t0].[EmployeeId], [t0].[DepartmentId], [t0].[DepartmentId0], [t1].[DepartmentId], [t1].[EmployeeId], [t1].[DepartmentId0]
FROM [Employees] AS [e]
INNER JOIN [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [d].[EmployeeId]
INNER JOIN [Designations] AS [d0] ON [e].[DesignationId] = [d0].[DesignationId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d2].[DepartmentName], [d1].[EmployeeId], [d1].[DepartmentId], [d2].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]
    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d1]
    INNER JOIN [Departments] AS [d2] ON [d1].[DepartmentId] = [d2].[DepartmentId]
) AS [t] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t].[EmployeeId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d4].[DepartmentCode], [d3].[EmployeeId], [d3].[DepartmentId], [d4].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]
    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d3]
    INNER JOIN [Departments] AS [d4] ON [d3].[DepartmentId] = [d4].[DepartmentId]
) AS [t0] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t0].[EmployeeId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d6].[DepartmentId], [d5].[EmployeeId], [d5].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]

) AS [t1] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t1].[EmployeeId]

SELECT [e].[EmployeeId], [e].[EmployeeName], [e].[EmployeeAddress], [e].[EmployeeSalary], [d0].[DesignationName], [d0].[DesignationCode], [e].[DesignationId], [d].[EmployeeId], [d].[DepartmentId], [d0].[DesignationId], [t].[DepartmentName], [t].[EmployeeId], [t].[DepartmentId], [t].[DepartmentId0], [t0].[DepartmentCode], [t0].[EmployeeId], [t0].[DepartmentId], [t0].[DepartmentId0], [t1].[DepartmentId], [t1].[EmployeeId], [t1].[DepartmentId0]
FROM [Employees] AS [e]
INNER JOIN [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [d].[EmployeeId]
INNER JOIN [Designations] AS [d0] ON [e].[DesignationId] = [d0].[DesignationId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d2].[DepartmentName], [d1].[EmployeeId], [d1].[DepartmentId], [d2].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]
    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d1]
    INNER JOIN [Departments] AS [d2] ON [d1].[DepartmentId] = [d2].[DepartmentId]
) AS [t] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t].[EmployeeId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d4].[DepartmentCode], [d3].[EmployeeId], [d3].[DepartmentId], [d4].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]
    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d3]
    INNER JOIN [Departments] AS [d4] ON [d3].[DepartmentId] = [d4].[DepartmentId]
) AS [t0] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t0].[EmployeeId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d6].[DepartmentId], [d5].[EmployeeId], [d5].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]
    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d5]
    INNER JOIN [Departments] AS [d6] ON [d5].[DepartmentId] = [d6].[DepartmentId]
) AS [t1] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t1].[EmployeeId]
ORDER BY [e].[EmployeeId], [d].[EmployeeId], [d].[DepartmentId], [d0].[DesignationId], [t].[EmployeeId], [t].[DepartmentId], [t].[DepartmentId0], [t0].[EmployeeId], [t0].[DepartmentId], [t0].[DepartmentId0], [t1].[EmployeeId], [t1].[DepartmentId0], [t1].[DepartmentId]

FROM [Employees] AS [e]
INNER JOIN [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [d].[EmployeeId]
INNER JOIN [Designations] AS [d0] ON [e].[DesignationId] = [d0].[DesignationId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d2].[DepartmentName], [d1].[EmployeeId], [d1].[DepartmentId], [d2].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]
    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d1]

) AS [t] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t].[EmployeeId]

SELECT [e].[EmployeeId], [e].[EmployeeName], [e].[EmployeeAddress], [e].[EmployeeSalary], [d0].[DesignationName], [d0].[DesignationCode], [e].[DesignationId], [d].[EmployeeId], [d].[DepartmentId], [d0].[DesignationId], [t].[DepartmentName], [t].[EmployeeId], [t].[DepartmentId], [t].[DepartmentId0], [t0].[DepartmentCode], [t0].[EmployeeId], [t0].[DepartmentId], [t0].[DepartmentId0], [t1].[DepartmentId], [t1].[EmployeeId], [t1].[DepartmentId0]
FROM [Employees] AS [e]
INNER JOIN [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [d].[EmployeeId]
INNER JOIN [Designations] AS [d0] ON [e].[DesignationId] = [d0].[DesignationId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d2].[DepartmentName], [d1].[EmployeeId], [d1].[DepartmentId], [d2].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]
    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d1]
    INNER JOIN [Departments] AS [d2] ON [d1].[DepartmentId] = [d2].[DepartmentId]
) AS [t] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t].[EmployeeId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d4].[DepartmentCode], [d3].[EmployeeId], [d3].[DepartmentId], [d4].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]
    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d3]
    INNER JOIN [Departments] AS [d4] ON [d3].[DepartmentId] = [d4].[DepartmentId]
) AS [t0] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t0].[EmployeeId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d6].[DepartmentId], [d5].[EmployeeId], [d5].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]
    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d5]
    INNER JOIN [Departments] AS [d6] ON [d5].[DepartmentId] = [d6].[DepartmentId]
) AS [t1] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t1].[EmployeeId]
ORDER BY [e].[EmployeeId], [d].[EmployeeId], [d].[DepartmentId], [d0].[DesignationId], [t].[EmployeeId], [t].[DepartmentId], [t].[DepartmentId0], [t0].[EmployeeId], [t0].[DepartmentId], [t0].[DepartmentId0], [t1].[EmployeeId], [t1].[DepartmentId0], [t1].[DepartmentId]

SELECT [e].[EmployeeId], [e].[EmployeeName], [e].[EmployeeAddress], [e].[EmployeeSalary], [d0].[DesignationName], [d0].[DesignationCode], [e].[DesignationId], [d].[EmployeeId], [d].[DepartmentId], [d0].[DesignationId], [t].[DepartmentName], [t].[EmployeeId], [t].[DepartmentId], [t].[DepartmentId0], [t0].[DepartmentCode], [t0].[EmployeeId], [t0].[DepartmentId], [t0].[DepartmentId0], [t1].[DepartmentId], [t1].[EmployeeId], [t1].[DepartmentId0]
FROM [Employees] AS [e]
INNER JOIN [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [d].[EmployeeId]
INNER JOIN [Designations] AS [d0] ON [e].[DesignationId] = [d0].[DesignationId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d2].[DepartmentName], [d1].[EmployeeId], [d1].[DepartmentId], [d2].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]
    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d1]
    INNER JOIN [Departments] AS [d2] ON [d1].[DepartmentId] = [d2].[DepartmentId]
) AS [t] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t].[EmployeeId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d4].[DepartmentCode], [d3].[EmployeeId], [d3].[DepartmentId], [d4].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]
    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d3]
    INNER JOIN [Departments] AS [d4] ON [d3].[DepartmentId] = [d4].[DepartmentId]
) AS [t0] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t0].[EmployeeId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d6].[DepartmentId], [d5].[EmployeeId], [d5].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]
    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d5]
    INNER JOIN [Departments] AS [d6] ON [d5].[DepartmentId] = [d6].[DepartmentId]
) AS [t1] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t1].[EmployeeId]
ORDER BY [e].[EmployeeId], [d].[EmployeeId], [d].[DepartmentId], [d0].[DesignationId], [t].[EmployeeId], [t].[DepartmentId], [t].[DepartmentId0], [t0].[EmployeeId], [t0].[DepartmentId], [t0].[DepartmentId0], [t1].[EmployeeId], [t1].[DepartmentId0], [t1].[DepartmentId]

INNER JOIN [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [d].[EmployeeId]
INNER JOIN [Designations] AS [d0] ON [e].[DesignationId] = [d0].[DesignationId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d2].[DepartmentName], [d1].[EmployeeId], [d1].[DepartmentId], [d2].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]
    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d1]
    INNER JOIN [Departments] AS [d2] ON [d1].[DepartmentId] = [d2].[DepartmentId]
) AS [t] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t].[EmployeeId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d4].[DepartmentCode], [d3].[EmployeeId], [d3].[DepartmentId], [d4].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]
    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d3]
    INNER JOIN [Departments] AS [d4] ON [d3].[DepartmentId] = [d4].[DepartmentId]
) AS [t0] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t0].[EmployeeId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d6].[DepartmentId], [d5].[EmployeeId], [d5].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]
    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d5]
    INNER JOIN [Departments] AS [d6] ON [d5].[DepartmentId] = [d6].[DepartmentId]
) AS [t1] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t1].[EmployeeId]
ORDER BY [e].[EmployeeId], [d].[EmployeeId], [d].[DepartmentId], [d0].[DesignationId], [t].[EmployeeId], [t].[DepartmentId], [t].[DepartmentId0], [t0].[EmployeeId], [t0].[DepartmentId], [t0].[DepartmentId0], [t1].[EmployeeId], [t1].[DepartmentId0], [t1].[DepartmentId]

SELECT [e].[EmployeeId], [e].[EmployeeName], [e].[EmployeeAddress], [e].[EmployeeSalary], [d0].[DesignationName], [d0].[DesignationCode], [e].[DesignationId], [d].[EmployeeId], [d].[DepartmentId], [d0].[DesignationId], [t].[DepartmentName], [t].[EmployeeId], [t].[DepartmentId], [t].[DepartmentId0], [t0].[DepartmentCode], [t0].[EmployeeId], [t0].[DepartmentId], [t0].[DepartmentId0], [t1].[DepartmentId], [t1].[EmployeeId], [t1].[DepartmentId0]
FROM [Employees] AS [e]
INNER JOIN [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [d].[EmployeeId]
INNER JOIN [Designations] AS [d0] ON [e].[DesignationId] = [d0].[DesignationId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d2].[DepartmentName], [d1].[EmployeeId], [d1].[DepartmentId], [d2].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]
    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d1]
    INNER JOIN [Departments] AS [d2] ON [d1].[DepartmentId] = [d2].[DepartmentId]
) AS [t] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t].[EmployeeId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d4].[DepartmentCode], [d3].[EmployeeId], [d3].[DepartmentId], [d4].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]
    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d3]

) AS [t0] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t0].[EmployeeId]

SELECT [e].[EmployeeId], [e].[EmployeeName], [e].[EmployeeAddress], [e].[EmployeeSalary], [d0].[DesignationName], [d0].[DesignationCode], [e].[DesignationId], [d].[EmployeeId], [d].[DepartmentId], [d0].[DesignationId], [t].[DepartmentName], [t].[EmployeeId], [t].[DepartmentId], [t].[DepartmentId0], [t0].[DepartmentCode], [t0].[EmployeeId], [t0].[DepartmentId], [t0].[DepartmentId0], [t1].[DepartmentId], [t1].[EmployeeId], [t1].[DepartmentId0]
FROM [Employees] AS [e]
INNER JOIN [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [d].[EmployeeId]
INNER JOIN [Designations] AS [d0] ON [e].[DesignationId] = [d0].[DesignationId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d2].[DepartmentName], [d1].[EmployeeId], [d1].[DepartmentId], [d2].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]
    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d1]
    INNER JOIN [Departments] AS [d2] ON [d1].[DepartmentId] = [d2].[DepartmentId]
) AS [t] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t].[EmployeeId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d4].[DepartmentCode], [d3].[EmployeeId], [d3].[DepartmentId], [d4].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]
    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d3]
    INNER JOIN [Departments] AS [d4] ON [d3].[DepartmentId] = [d4].[DepartmentId]
) AS [t0] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t0].[EmployeeId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d6].[DepartmentId], [d5].[EmployeeId], [d5].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]
    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d5]

        outerKeySelector: employee => employee.EmployeeId, 
        innerKeySelector: EmployeeDepartment => EmployeeDepartment.EmployeeId, 
        resultSelector: (employee, EmployeeDepartment) => new GetAllEmployeesDTO{ 
            EmployeeId = employee.EmployeeId, 
            EmployeeName = employee.EmployeeName, 
            EmployeeAddress = employee.EmployeeAddress, 
            EmployeeSalary = employee.EmployeeSalary, 
            DesignationName = employee.Designation.DesignationName, 
            DesignationCode = employee.Designation.DesignationCode, 
            DepartmentName = DbSet<DepartmentEmployee>()
                .Where(departmentEmployee => departmentEmployee.EmployeeId == employee.EmployeeId)
                .Select(employee => employee.Department.DepartmentName)
                .ToList(), 
            DepartmentCode = DbSet<DepartmentEmployee>()
                .Where(departmentEmployee => departmentEmployee.EmployeeId == employee.EmployeeId)
                .Select(employee => employee.Department.DepartmentCode)
                .ToList(), 
            DepartmentIds = DbSet<DepartmentEmployee>()
                .Where(departmentEmployee => departmentEmployee.EmployeeId == employee.EmployeeId)
                .Select(employee => employee.Department.DepartmentId)
                .ToList(), 
            DesignationId = employee.DesignationId 
        }
    )'

INNER JOIN [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [d].[EmployeeId]
INNER JOIN [Designations] AS [d0] ON [e].[DesignationId] = [d0].[DesignationId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d2].[DepartmentName], [d1].[EmployeeId], [d1].[DepartmentId], [d2].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]

FROM [Employees] AS [e]
INNER JOIN [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [d].[EmployeeId]
INNER JOIN [Designations] AS [d0] ON [e].[DesignationId] = [d0].[DesignationId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d2].[DepartmentName], [d1].[EmployeeId], [d1].[DepartmentId], [d2].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]
    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d1]
    INNER JOIN [Departments] AS [d2] ON [d1].[DepartmentId] = [d2].[DepartmentId]
) AS [t] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t].[EmployeeId]

) AS [t0] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t0].[EmployeeId]

) AS [t1] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t1].[EmployeeId]

    INNER JOIN [Departments] AS [d4] ON [d3].[DepartmentId] = [d4].[DepartmentId]
) AS [t0] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t0].[EmployeeId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d6].[DepartmentId], [d5].[EmployeeId], [d5].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]
    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d5]
    INNER JOIN [Departments] AS [d6] ON [d5].[DepartmentId] = [d6].[DepartmentId]
) AS [t1] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t1].[EmployeeId]
ORDER BY [e].[EmployeeId], [d].[EmployeeId], [d].[DepartmentId], [d0].[DesignationId], [t].[EmployeeId], [t].[DepartmentId], [t].[DepartmentId0], [t0].[EmployeeId], [t0].[DepartmentId], [t0].[DepartmentId0], [t1].[EmployeeId], [t1].[DepartmentId0], [t1].[DepartmentId]

INNER JOIN [Designations] AS [d0] ON [e].[DesignationId] = [d0].[DesignationId]

FROM [Employees] AS [e]
INNER JOIN [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [d].[EmployeeId]
INNER JOIN [Designations] AS [d0] ON [e].[DesignationId] = [d0].[DesignationId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d2].[DepartmentName], [d1].[EmployeeId], [d1].[DepartmentId], [d2].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]

) AS [t] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t].[EmployeeId]

) AS [t0] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t0].[EmployeeId]

) AS [t1] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t1].[EmployeeId]

SELECT [e].[EmployeeId], [e].[EmployeeName], [e].[EmployeeAddress], [e].[EmployeeSalary], [d0].[DesignationName], [d0].[DesignationCode], [e].[DesignationId], [d].[EmployeeId], [d].[DepartmentId], [d0].[DesignationId], [t].[DepartmentName], [t].[EmployeeId], [t].[DepartmentId], [t].[DepartmentId0], [t0].[DepartmentCode], [t0].[EmployeeId], [t0].[DepartmentId], [t0].[DepartmentId0], [t1].[DepartmentId], [t1].[EmployeeId], [t1].[DepartmentId0]
FROM [Employees] AS [e]
INNER JOIN [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [d].[EmployeeId]
INNER JOIN [Designations] AS [d0] ON [e].[DesignationId] = [d0].[DesignationId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d2].[DepartmentName], [d1].[EmployeeId], [d1].[DepartmentId], [d2].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]
    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d1]
    INNER JOIN [Departments] AS [d2] ON [d1].[DepartmentId] = [d2].[DepartmentId]
) AS [t] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t].[EmployeeId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d4].[DepartmentCode], [d3].[EmployeeId], [d3].[DepartmentId], [d4].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]
    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d3]
    INNER JOIN [Departments] AS [d4] ON [d3].[DepartmentId] = [d4].[DepartmentId]
) AS [t0] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t0].[EmployeeId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d6].[DepartmentId], [d5].[EmployeeId], [d5].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]
    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d5]
    INNER JOIN [Departments] AS [d6] ON [d5].[DepartmentId] = [d6].[DepartmentId]
) AS [t1] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t1].[EmployeeId]
ORDER BY [e].[EmployeeId], [d].[EmployeeId], [d].[DepartmentId], [d0].[DesignationId], [t].[EmployeeId], [t].[DepartmentId], [t].[DepartmentId0], [t0].[EmployeeId], [t0].[DepartmentId], [t0].[DepartmentId0], [t1].[EmployeeId], [t1].[DepartmentId0], [t1].[DepartmentId]

SELECT [e].[EmployeeId], [e].[EmployeeName], [e].[EmployeeAddress], [e].[EmployeeSalary], [d0].[DesignationName], [d0].[DesignationCode], [e].[DesignationId], [d].[EmployeeId], [d].[DepartmentId], [d0].[DesignationId], [t].[DepartmentName], [t].[EmployeeId], [t].[DepartmentId], [t].[DepartmentId0], [t0].[DepartmentCode], [t0].[EmployeeId], [t0].[DepartmentId], [t0].[DepartmentId0], [t1].[DepartmentId], [t1].[EmployeeId], [t1].[DepartmentId0]
FROM [Employees] AS [e]
INNER JOIN [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [d].[EmployeeId]
INNER JOIN [Designations] AS [d0] ON [e].[DesignationId] = [d0].[DesignationId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d2].[DepartmentName], [d1].[EmployeeId], [d1].[DepartmentId], [d2].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]
    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d1]
    INNER JOIN [Departments] AS [d2] ON [d1].[DepartmentId] = [d2].[DepartmentId]
) AS [t] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t].[EmployeeId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d4].[DepartmentCode], [d3].[EmployeeId], [d3].[DepartmentId], [d4].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]
    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d3]
    INNER JOIN [Departments] AS [d4] ON [d3].[DepartmentId] = [d4].[DepartmentId]
) AS [t0] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t0].[EmployeeId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d6].[DepartmentId], [d5].[EmployeeId], [d5].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]
    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d5]
    INNER JOIN [Departments] AS [d6] ON [d5].[DepartmentId] = [d6].[DepartmentId]
) AS [t1] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t1].[EmployeeId]
ORDER BY [e].[EmployeeId], [d].[EmployeeId], [d].[DepartmentId], [d0].[DesignationId], [t].[EmployeeId], [t].[DepartmentId], [t].[DepartmentId0], [t0].[EmployeeId], [t0].[DepartmentId], [t0].[DepartmentId0], [t1].[EmployeeId], [t1].[DepartmentId0], [t1].[DepartmentId]

SELECT [e].[EmployeeId], [e].[EmployeeName], [e].[EmployeeAddress], [e].[EmployeeSalary], [d0].[DesignationName], [d0].[DesignationCode], [e].[DesignationId], [d].[EmployeeId], [d].[DepartmentId], [d0].[DesignationId], [t].[DepartmentName], [t].[EmployeeId], [t].[DepartmentId], [t].[DepartmentId0], [t0].[DepartmentCode], [t0].[EmployeeId], [t0].[DepartmentId], [t0].[DepartmentId0], [t1].[DepartmentId], [t1].[EmployeeId], [t1].[DepartmentId0]
FROM [Employees] AS [e]
INNER JOIN [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [d].[EmployeeId]
INNER JOIN [Designations] AS [d0] ON [e].[DesignationId] = [d0].[DesignationId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d2].[DepartmentName], [d1].[EmployeeId], [d1].[DepartmentId], [d2].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]
    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d1]
    INNER JOIN [Departments] AS [d2] ON [d1].[DepartmentId] = [d2].[DepartmentId]
) AS [t] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t].[EmployeeId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d4].[DepartmentCode], [d3].[EmployeeId], [d3].[DepartmentId], [d4].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]
    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d3]
    INNER JOIN [Departments] AS [d4] ON [d3].[DepartmentId] = [d4].[DepartmentId]
) AS [t0] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t0].[EmployeeId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d6].[DepartmentId], [d5].[EmployeeId], [d5].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]
    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d5]
    INNER JOIN [Departments] AS [d6] ON [d5].[DepartmentId] = [d6].[DepartmentId]
) AS [t1] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t1].[EmployeeId]

FROM [Employees] AS [e]
INNER JOIN [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [d].[EmployeeId]
INNER JOIN [Designations] AS [d0] ON [e].[DesignationId] = [d0].[DesignationId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d2].[DepartmentName], [d1].[EmployeeId], [d1].[DepartmentId], [d2].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]
    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d1]
    INNER JOIN [Departments] AS [d2] ON [d1].[DepartmentId] = [d2].[DepartmentId]
) AS [t] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t].[EmployeeId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d4].[DepartmentCode], [d3].[EmployeeId], [d3].[DepartmentId], [d4].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]
    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d3]
    INNER JOIN [Departments] AS [d4] ON [d3].[DepartmentId] = [d4].[DepartmentId]
) AS [t0] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t0].[EmployeeId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d6].[DepartmentId], [d5].[EmployeeId], [d5].[DepartmentId] AS [DepartmentId0]
    FROM [DepartmentEmployees] AS [d5]

) AS [t1] ON [e].[EmployeeId] = [t1].[EmployeeId]
